description:
This is a 8 minute workout called 'Morning Breathwork Practice' from the channel Kirsten McCormick.
The workout falls under Rest/Breathing exercises.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Zen Flow and The Deep Recharge vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Use this gentle morning breath practice to start the day with an clear, calm, and energized mind. Start your day confidently knowing you were able to dedicate 7 minutes purely to connecting to your breath and body and knowing that you have the power to connect and be productive with your own thoughts and actions....
